616
00:38:33.481 --> 00:38:34.899
There's something wrong with my semen.

617
00:38:34.899 --> 00:38:36.526
That reminds me. what you gonna name it?

618
00:38:38.028 --> 00:38:40.447
Ed. Ed Junior.

619
