I was only trying to help!

708
00:42:28.966 --> 00:42:32.512
You crazy! You're crazy. man!

709
00:42:32.554 --> 00:42:35.349
Keep your goddamn hands off my wife!

710
00:42:35.391 --> 00:42:37.685
You're crazy! I pity you!

711
