He was provoking me.

718
00:43:07.351 --> 00:43:08.519
How?

719
00:43:12.233 --> 00:43:13.359
Never mind.

720
00:43:13.401 --> 00:43:17.990
But. Hi. he's your foreman. He's gonna fire you now.

721
00:43:19.117 --> 00:43:20.744
I expect he will.

722
00:43:20.786 --> 00:43:22.204
And where does that leave the three of us?

723
00:43:22.246 --> 00:43:24.373
Where does that leave our entire family unit?

724
00:43:28.922 --> 00:43:30.590
With a man for a husband.

725
00:43:30.632 --> 00:43:32.426
That ain't no answer.

726
00:43:33.845 --> 00:43:35.722
Honey. that's the only answer.

727
00:43:35.764 --> 00:43:36.890
That ain't no answer.

728
00:43:36.933 --> 00:43:38.768
Just a man for a husband.

729
