That sumbitch.

741
00:44:37.890 --> 00:44:39.850
That son of a bitch.

742
00:44:44.858 --> 00:44:46.485
You son of a bitch!

743
00:44:46.527 --> 00:44:48.905
Hurry up. I'm in Dutch with the wife.

744
00:44:49.739 --> 00:44:51.074
You son of a bitch!

745
00:44:52.952 --> 00:44:54.203
Come on. now.

746
