755
00:47:37.180 --> 00:47:39.641
Aah! Can I stop now?

756
00:47:47.611 --> 00:47:48.779
Thank you.

757
00:47:53.870 --> 00:47:55.664
That's private property. son.

758
00:47:55.706 --> 00:47:59.878
