759
00:48:11.187 --> 00:48:12.605
Son of a bitch.

760
00:49:36.976 --> 00:49:40.063
Thank you. honey. but you really didn't have to do this.

761
00:49:40.106 --> 00:49:43.152
You son of a bitch! What if we'd been picked up?

762
00:49:43.193 --> 00:49:44.361
