and I think you better had. too.

773
00:50:05.350 --> 00:50:09.397
I'm OK. you're OK. That there's what it is.

774
00:50:09.439 --> 00:50:11.274
I know. but. honey...

775
00:50:11.317 --> 00:50:13.194
